            "answer_text": "You can not learn machine learning in limited time. It is a continues effort. The whole subject is very fast and new algorithms and technique keep coming out everyday. One thing that you should focus on is learning all the basics and how these are applied in ML. It includes basically: 1. Probability and statistics2. Linear algebra3. Optimization theory4. Good coding skills Depending on person, mastering above things can take anything between 6 months to 2 years. ",
